31798	31798	channel between islands. A narrow passage of water between two islands or landmasses.	島間の水路、海峡。二つの島や陸地の間にある狭い水路。	Mibiyahe ang bangka sa sapang tali sa duha ka pulo.
31799	31799	small wooden fishing boat. A small, simply constructed wooden boat used for near-shore fishing.	小型の木造漁船。沿岸漁業に使われる簡素な造りの小型木造船。	Gigamit niya ang tabako-tabako sa baybayon.
