31801	31801	sea pirate, bandit at sea. A criminal who attacks boats and fishermen at sea.	海賊、海上の賊。海上で船や漁師を襲う犯罪者。	Nahadlok sila sa tulisan sa lawod.
31802	31802	to haul, to pull in a net. To drag or pull in a fishing net loaded with the catch.	網を引き上げる、網を手繰る。漁獲物の入った漁網を引きずって引き上げること。	Gihila nila ang pukot nga puno sa isda.
