31814	31814	fathom, arm span measurement. A measurement equal to the span of two outstretched arms, about 6 feet.	ひろ（尋）、両腕を広げた長さの単位。両腕を伸ばした幅に相当する約6フィートの長さの単位。	Napulo ka dipa ang giladmon sa pangisda nila.
31815	31815	last night, night fishing time. The previous night, often referenced in discussing night fishing.	昨夜、夜釣りの時間帯。前の夜のこと。夜釣りに関する話題でよく使われる。	Kagab-i, dako ang ilang kuha sa pangulat.
31816	31816	calm, flat (of the sea). Describes a sea surface that is smooth and without waves.	（海が）穏やか、凪いでいる。波がなく海面が滑らかな状態を表す。	Napintas ang dagat ugma busa malawig ta.
31817	31817	choppy sea, rough waves. Sea conditions with many small irregular waves making travel difficult.	波立つ海、荒れた波。小さく不規則な波が多く、航行を困難にする海の状態。	Bangbangas ang dagat sa ting-habagat karon.
31818	31818	fishing season, productive period. A known period of the year when certain fish are abundant.	漁期、魚がよく獲れる時期。特定の魚が豊富に獲れることで知られる年間の時期。	Ang sinalig sa bariles sa Agosto ug Septyembre.
31819	31819	fishing ground. A specific area of sea known to be productive for fishing.	漁場。漁に適した海域として知られる特定の場所。	Ang ilang pangisdaanan naa sa duha ka oras gikan sa baybayon.
31820	31820	to drift, to be carried by current. To be carried away by wind or water current without control.	漂流する、潮流に流される。風や水流に制御なく運ばれること。	Napalid ang bangka sa kusog nga agos.
31821	31821	boat captain, skipper. The person in command of a fishing boat or vessel.	船長、スキッパー。漁船や船舶を指揮する人物。	Ang kaptan nagmando sa tibuok biyahe sa lawod.
31822	31822	planting season, growing season. The period of the year when crops are planted and grown.	植え付け期、成長期。作物を植えて育てる年間の時期。	Mag-andam na kita sa tingtubo kay hapit na mag-ulan.
31823	31823	barren, infertile land. Describes land that cannot support plant growth due to poor soil quality.	不毛な、痩せた土地。土壌の質が悪く植物の生育を支えられない土地を表す。	Baog ang yuta sa bukid, dili maayo alang sa uma.
31824	31824	seedbed, nursery bed. Small prepared plot where seeds are first germinated before transplanting.	苗床、育苗床。移植前に種を発芽させるために用意された小さな区画。	Giandam ang punlan sa kilid sa uma para sa palay.
