31864	31864	to test soil readiness for planting. The practice of testing soil conditions to determine planting suitability.	播種に向けた土壌の準備状態を調べる。植え付けの適否を判断するために土壌の状態を確認する行為。	Gihibawon niya ang yuta aron mahibalo kung andam na sa pagtanom.
