23359	23359	Chinese white cabbage. Alternate spelling of pechay, a leafy vegetable used in many dishes.	白菜（チンゲン菜）。ペチャイの別表記で、多くの料理に使われる葉野菜。	Gibuang niya ang petsay sa pancit guisado.
23360	23360	winged bean pods. Alternate spelling for sigarilyas, the four-winged pod legume.	シカクマメのさや。シガリリャスの別表記で、四つの翼のあるさや豆。	Gibulag niya ang sigarillas para sa guisado.
