23408	23408	pomegranate fruit. Round red fruit with many juicy red seed-like arils inside thick skin.	ザクロ。厚い皮の中に多数の赤い果汁たっぷりの種が詰まった丸い赤い果物。	Gipalit niya ang granada sa imported fruits section sa grocery.
