23414	23414	is ripening, becoming ripe. Refers to the process of fruit gradually becoming ripe on or off the tree.	熟しつつある、熟してきている。果物が木の上またはそこから離れて徐々に熟していく過程を表す。	Nanghinog na ang mga mangga sa kahoy sa among silingan.
23415	23415	to pick fruit, to harvest. Action of picking or harvesting fruit from a tree or plant.	果物を摘む、収穫する。木や植物から果物を摘み取ったり収穫したりする動作。	Mipitas siya og saging gikan sa kahoy sa ilang natad.
23416	23416	picked fruit, was harvesting. Past tense form indicating someone was picking fruit from a plant.	果物を摘んだ、収穫していた。誰かが植物から果物を摘んでいたことを示す過去形。	Nagpitas ang mga bata og aratilis didto sa gilid sa dalan.
23417	23417	will pick, to be picked. Future tense form of pitas, indicating fruit that will be harvested.	摘む予定、摘み取られる予定。収穫される果物を示すピタスの未来形。	Pitason na nako ang mga santol ugma buntag.
23418	23418	to go fruit picking. Going out specifically to pick or gather fruits from trees or plants.	果物摘みに行く。木や植物から果物を摘みに特に出かけること。	Mamita kita og lansones ugma sa uma ni Tatay.
23419	23419	fruit with edible root or rhizome. Refers broadly to plant parts including fruit-bearing roots eaten as food.	食用の根や根茎を持つ植物。食用にされる果実をつける根を含む植物の部位を広く指す。	Lain-lain ang ginamot ug prutas nga gibaligya sa palengke.
