23551	23551	loose soil for root crops. Soft, crumbly soil that is ideal for growing root vegetables.	根菜向けのやわらかい土。根菜の栽培に適した柔らかくほろほろした土。	Kinahanglan og yuta-yuta para motubo ang kamote.
23552	23552	to thresh grain by beating. To beat harvested stalks against a hard surface to release grains.	穂を打ちつけて脱穀する。収穫した茎を硬い面に打ちつけて穀粒を取り出す。	Ginahampak nila ang humay sa kahoy aron malabasan.
