23561	23561	pounded smooth. Describing grain or root crop that has been pounded to a smooth texture.	滑らかにすりつぶした。穀物や根菜を滑らかな状態になるまでついたことを表す。	Nilusok na ang gabi, puwede nang gamiton sa tinumok.
