25279	25279	rinse water. Clean water used for rinsing soap or detergent from clothes or dishes.	すすぎ水。衣類や食器から石鹸や洗剤を洗い流すためのきれいな水。	Dugangan pa ang tabang-tubig para mawala ang sabon.
25280	25280	rinse; rinsing action. The process of washing away soap residue with clean water.	すすぎ・すすぎ動作。きれいな水で石鹸の残留物を洗い流す工程。	Pag-ablisyon sa mga pinggan human sabona.
25281	25281	to rinse mouth or gargle. The act of rinsing or gargling the mouth with water or mouthwash.	口をすすぐ・うがいをする。水やマウスウォッシュで口をすすいだりうがいをする行為。	Luaga ang imo baba human sipilyo.
