24335	24335	food to be eaten with rice. Any food specifically intended to be eaten together with rice.	ご飯と一緒に食べるもの。ご飯と共に食べることを前提とした食べ物全般。	Unsa may kan-onon nato karong pamahaw?
24336	24336	glutinous rice, sticky rice. Sticky variety of rice that becomes very adhesive when cooked.	もち米、糯米。炊くと非常に粘り気が出るもち種の米。	Ang pilit ginagamit sa pagbuhat og suman ug biko.
