25330	25330	cleaner; janitor. A person whose job is to clean homes or establishments.	清掃員・用務員。家庭や施設を清掃することを仕事とする人。	Ang manglimpyo moabot matag Sabado sa opisina.
25331	25331	liquid soap. Soap in liquid form, typically used in dispensers for handwashing.	液体石鹸。ディスペンサーに入れて手洗いに使う液状の石鹸。	Gitipigan ang sabon-likido sa dispenser.
