24382	24382	coconut milk curds, rice cake topping. Browned coconut milk residue used as topping for biko and other rice cakes.	ラティック、米菓子のトッピング。ビコなどの米菓子にかける、焦がしたココナッツミルクの残り滓。	Gibutangan niya og latik ang biko para dugang lami.
