24415	24415	lament over lack of rice. The expression of sorrow or lament when there is not enough rice to eat.	米不足への嘆き。食べるための米が足りない時に表す悲しみや嘆きの表現。	Adunay taghoy ang inahan tungod kay wala nay kan-on ang pamilya.
24416	24416	nutrition from rice and food. Nutritional content and health benefits derived from eating rice.	米や食品の栄養素。米を食べることから得られる栄養成分と健康上の効能。	Ang kan-on adunay sustansya nga naghatag og kusog sa lawas.
24417	24417	meat braised in vinegar and soy sauce. A popular dish of meat cooked in vinegar, soy sauce, garlic, and bay leaf.	アドボ。肉を酢・醤油・ニンニク・ローリエで煮込んだ人気料理。	Niluto siya og adobo nga manok para sa paniudto.
