24701	24701	variant of battered fried egg snack. Another spelling of tokneneng, a battered deep-fried egg street food.	トゥクネネン。衣揚げ卵スナックの別表記。衣をつけて揚げた卵のストリートフード「トクネネン」の別のつづり。	Nagpalit ang bata ug tukneneng sa labas sa eskwelahan.
