24719	24719	coconut milk cooked dish. Any dish cooked in coconut milk, whether sweet or savory.	ギナタン。ヤシミルク料理。ヤシミルクで調理した甘口・塩味いずれかの料理の総称。	Ang ginat-an nga ube ug saging lami kaayo isip dessert.
