24721	24721	delicious, savory and tasty. Describes food with a deep, satisfying and irresistible flavor.	深みがあって食欲をそそるほどの美味しさで、旨みが強くやみつきになる味を表す形容詞。	Malinamnam kaayo ang dinuguan uban ang puto.
