24733	24733	mutant coconut sweet preserve. A special type of coconut with abnormal soft flesh often made into a sweet preserve used in desserts.	マカプノ。変種ヤシの砂糖漬け。柔らかい異常果肉を持つ特殊なヤシで、甘い砂糖漬けに加工されてデザートの材料として使われる。	Ang macapuno usa sa akong paboritong topping sa halo-halo.
24734	24734	sweetened shredded coconut candy. A traditional Filipino candy made from shredded young coconut cooked in sugar until caramelized.	ブカヨ。甘いヤシの実千切りキャンディー。若いヤシの実を細切りにして砂糖でカラメル状になるまで炊いた伝統的な菓子。	Gibaligya ang bukayo sa tiangge sa plasa.
24735	24735	raw sugarcane block candy. A traditional hard candy made from molded unrefined sugarcane juice, common in Cebu and Negros.	パノチャ。サトウキビ粗糖の固形キャンディー。未精製のサトウキビ汁を型に流して固めた伝統的な硬い飴で、セブやネグロス島に多い。	Gihatag sa lolo ang panocha sa mga bata ingon nga merienda.
