24737	24737	small glutinous rice flour balls. Tiny balls made from glutinous rice flour added to various coconut milk-based desserts.	ビロビロ。小さな白玉粉の団子。白玉粉で作る小さな丸い団子で、ヤシミルクベースのさまざまなデザートに加えて使われる。	Gihinog ang bilo-bilo sa tambok nga gata.
