24739	24739	thin rolled wafer cookie sweet. Thin, crispy rolled wafer cookies made from flour, eggs, and sugar, a Cebuano specialty.	バルキジョス。薄巻きウエハースクッキー。小麦粉・卵・砂糖で作られた薄くてサクサクの巻きウエハースで、セブの名物菓子。	Ang barquillos sikat nga pasalubong nga buhat sa Cebu.
