25586	25586	sturdy and strong farm implement. Describes a farming tool that is strong, durable, and hard-wearing.	丈夫で頑丈な農具。強くて耐久性が高く、長持ちする農具を表す形容詞。	Baskog ang iyang bag-ong arado.
