25592	25592	small outrigger fishing boat. A traditional wooden boat with outriggers used for fishing in coastal waters.	小型アウトリガー漁船。沿岸漁業に使われるアウトリガー付きの伝統的な木造船。	Gisakay nila ang banca ug miadto sa lawod.
