25595	25595	fishing industry, fishermen's group. Refers to the fishing community or the collective practice of fishing.	漁業、漁師の集団。漁業コミュニティ、または漁業という営みの総称。	Ang palakaya sa amon barangay gamhanan kaayo.
25596	25596	fisherman who uses traps. A person who specializes in using fish traps to catch fish.	罠漁師。魚罠を専門に使って魚を捕る人。	Ang magbabalat mao ang pinaka-daghan og nakuha sa barangay.
