25606	25606	fish corral, stake net. An enclosure made with stakes and nets in shallow coastal water to trap fish.	魚囲い・杭網。浅い沿岸の水中に杭と網で作った囲いで魚を閉じ込める漁具。	Daghan kaayo ang nakulong nga isda sa palunggo.
