25664	25664	fishing vessel, transport boat. A larger boat or vessel used for transporting fish and fishing gear.	漁船・輸送船。魚や漁具の輸送に使う大型の船または漁船。	Ang bag-ong sakyanan sa ila maoy gigamit sa malayong panagat.
25665	25665	to lie flat, flatten net in water. To spread or lay a net flat on the water surface or bottom.	網を水面または水底に平らに広げる。網を水面や水底に平らに展開して敷く。	Gidapa nila ang pukot sa may baba sa suba.
25666	25666	to pass through, pierce. For a fish to pass through or pierce through a net opening.	（魚が）網の目を通り抜ける。魚が網の目を通り抜けたり突き抜けたりすること。	Nakalagbas ang dako nga lapu-lapu sa pukot kay dako ang buho.
25667	25667	large spear for big fish. A heavy spear used for harpooning large fish or sea creatures.	大型魚用の大きな槍。大きな魚や海の生き物を突くために使う重い銛。	Gigamit nila ang sumbak sa pagpanagat og balyena-balyena.
28025	28025	careful, ensuring quality, thorough. Refers to someone who makes sure everything is done properly and completely.	慎重で質を確保し、徹底的な。すべてが正しく完全に行われるよう確認する人を指す。	Mapaniguro siya nga tanan nasangkapan sa proyekto.
28026	28026	principled, morally anchored, grounded. Refers to someone firmly grounded in good principles and moral values.	信念に基づき、道徳的に根ざした、しっかりした。優れた原則と道徳的価値観にしっかり根ざした人を指す。	Mapanalikala siya sa iyang mga pagtuo bisan pa sa impluwensya sa uban.
28027	28027	generous with food, hospitable in feeding. Refers to someone who is especially generous in sharing food with guests.	食事を分け与えることに寛大で、もてなし好きな。ゲストに食べ物を惜しみなく振る舞う人を指す。	Mapagmaon ang pamilya sa ilang pagpakaon sa mga bisita.
28028	28028	cherishing, warmly devoted, endearing. Describes someone who holds others in tender regard and cherishes them deeply.	大切にし、温かく献身的で、愛おしむ。他者を愛おしい存在として深く大切にする人を表す。	Mapinanggaon siya sa iyang mga anak ug apo.
28029	28029	participatory, collaborative, inclusive. Refers to someone who invites and includes others in decisions and activities.	参加を促し、協力的で包括的な。意思決定や活動に他者を招き入れる人を指す。	Mapakigbahin siya sa iyang estilo sa pamunoan sa kooperatiba.
28030	28030	servant-hearted, ministering, serving. Describes someone who naturally and willingly takes on the role of servant to others.	奉仕の心を持ち、仕えることを厭わない。自然と進んで他者に仕える役割を担う人を表す。	Maalagad siya sa iyang simbahan matag Domingo.
28031	28031	action-oriented for good, actively virtuous. Refers to someone who translates good intentions into actual helpful actions.	善のために行動し、積極的に徳を実践する。良い意図を実際の助けとなる行動に移す人を指す。	Mabubuhaton siya sa iyang saad nga tabangan ang komunidad.
29742	29742	to wipe dry or clean. To wipe a surface clean, often to dry it.	拭き取る、乾拭きする。表面をきれいに拭く、特に乾かすために拭く。	Punas sa imong nawong gamit ang tuwalya.
28032	28032	understanding, comprehending, empathetic. Refers to someone who readily understands situations from another's perspective.	理解力があり、共感できる。他者の立場から状況を素直に理解する人を指す。	Mapanabot siya sa kahimtang sa iyang estudyante nga kabos.
28033	28033	transformative, able to change things for good. Refers to someone whose presence or work brings about positive transformation.	変革をもたらし、良い方向へ変える力を持つ。その存在や仕事が良い変化をもたらす人を指す。	Mapag-usab ang iyang pamaagi sa pagtutok sa kabataan.
