28035	28035	principled, acting on good principles. Refers to someone whose character is built on and guided by strong moral principles.	信念に基づき、良い原則に従って行動する。強固な道徳的原則を基盤に生きる人を指す。	Mapanigmalon siya sa iyang pamaagi sa negosyo ug pakig-uban.
28036	28036	protective, safeguarding others. Describes someone whose presence provides a sense of safety and protection.	保護的で他者を守る。その存在が安心感と保護をもたらす人を表す。	Maka-amping siya sa iyang mga manghod gikan sa mga peligro.
28037	28037	reconciling, peace-building, harmony-seeking. Refers to someone who actively works to restore harmony between conflicting parties.	和解を促し、調和を築く。対立する者の間に積極的に調和を取り戻す人を指す。	Mapagmahinaluyon siya sa iyang katungdanan isip mediator.
28038	28038	agreeable, harmonious, going along well. Refers to someone who fits in harmoniously with others in any group setting.	協調的で和を乱さない、うまく溶け込む。どんな集団にも調和よく馴染む人を指す。	Mapahiuyon siya sa bisan unsang grupo nga iyang sulod-on.
28039	28039	rude, vulgar, disrespectful. Describes someone who behaves without manners or decency.	無礼で下品、失礼な。礼儀や品位のない振る舞いをする人を表す。	Bastos ang bata kay wala nag-abi-abi sa tigulang.
28040	28040	lazy, idle. A shorter form describing a person who is habitually inactive.	怠け者で無精な。習慣的に活動しない人を表す簡潔な形。	Tapul si Pedro ug dili gusto magtrabaho.
