25681	25681	tide pool, low tide fishing area. A shallow area exposed during low tide where fish are trapped.	潮溜まり、干潮時漁場。干潮時に露出し魚が取り残される浅い場所。	Naglakaw sila sa hinubsan aron mangita og isda sa bata-batang tubig.
