26943	26943	dawn; very early morning. The very early part of morning before sunrise.	夜明け；早朝。日の出前の非常に早い朝の時間帯。	Mobangon siya sa kaadlawon aron manaad.
26944	26944	now; at this time. Refers to the present moment or current time.	今；現在。現在の瞬間または今の時点を指す。	Subong na ang oras sa pagkuha sa reseta.
26945	26945	half past; thirty minutes. Used to indicate thirty minutes past the hour.	半；30分。毎時30分を示すために使われる表現。	Alas dos medya na ang miting.
