28220	28220	graceful in walking, poised. Describes someone who walks with graceful and attractive movement.	歩き方が優雅な、姿勢が良い。優雅で美しい歩き方をする人を表す。	Lakaw-lakaw siya nga daw artista sa Hollywood.
