28234	28234	colorfully beautiful, vivid. Describes an attractive quality characterized by vivid and beautiful coloring.	色彩豊かで美しい、鮮やかな。鮮明で美しい色彩が特徴的な魅力的な質を表す。	Mamugna ang kinaiyahan sa isla pagkasalop sa adlaw.
