30588	30588	focus linker, topic marker. Ligature or focus particle linking topic to predicate in a sentence.	（焦点連結詞・主題標識）。文中で主題と述語をつなぐ焦点助詞。	Si Maria ay maisog.
30589	30589	emphasis, mild assertion, too. Enclitic particle adding mild emphasis or confirmation to a statement.	（強調・軽い断言）。文に軽い強調や確認のニュアンスを加える後接助詞。	Maayu man siya.
