31567	31567	man-to-man defense in basketball. A defense where each player guards a specific opponent.	バスケットボールのマンツーマンディフェンス。各選手が特定の相手を個別にマークする守備方式。	Man-to-man ang depensya nga gigamit sa championship finals.
