31584	31584	to have someone play music. Causative form meaning to let or cause someone to play an instrument.	誰かに楽器を演奏させること。他者に楽器を弾かせる使役的行為。	Gipatokar niya ang iyang anak og piano.
31585	31585	a folk dance style. A traditional Visayan dance characterized by graceful and flowing movements.	民族舞踊のスタイル。優雅で流れるような動きが特徴の伝統的なビサヤの踊り。	Ang inayaw gisayaw sa mga babaye sa baryo.
