31612	31612	traditional chant, ritual song. A rhythmic chant or poetic song used in traditional Visayan ceremonies.	伝統的な詠唱、儀礼歌。ビサヤの伝統的な儀式で用いられるリズミカルな詠唱や詩的な歌。	Giambit ang ambahan sa tigulang aron mangayo og gasa.
