31628	31628	costume, traditional attire. Traditional garments worn during cultural performances or festivals.	衣装、伝統的な服装。文化的な公演や祭りの際に着用される伝統的な衣装。	Ang kostumbra sa mananayaw pula ug bulawan ang kulay.
